        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer737257141" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15847947295074364468">Chima writes a family saga in which the characters are tragically doomed to shoulder the sins of their parents. Although the characters are at times frustratingly blind, I nonetheless understood their decisions and motives, cheering them in the right direction even when I knew they would veer off course. Exciting, it reads quickly despite its length, and kept me riveted until the end. A must read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


